00:40:37,422 --> 00:40:39,173
Maksudku, Pengacara Lee datang.

672
00:40:40,383 --> 00:40:41,301
Siapa?

673
00:40:41,384 --> 00:40:42,719
Lee Mi-do.

674
00:40:46,598 --> 00:40:48,182
Mi-do?

675
00:40:53,771 --> 00:40:54,856
Astaga.

