00:41:24,260 --> 00:41:26,012
Aku tak berpikir panjang.

686
00:41:29,098 --> 00:41:33,144
Omong-omong, aku kemari
untuk menanyakan sesuatu.

687
00:41:34,562 --> 00:41:36,105
Di hari Oh Yeong-cheol ditahan...

688
00:41:37,148 --> 00:41:37,982
Detektif Choe.

689
00:41:38,066 --> 00:41:42,028
Wanita ini punya pertanyaan
soal kasus Oh Yeong-cheol.

690
00:41:42,612 --> 00:41:43,571
Apa...

691
00:41:45,198 --> 00:41:47,408
Dia masih sedih?

692
00:41:47,950 --> 00:41:49,535
Pecundang itu...

693
00:41:53,247 --> 00:41:55,208
Jadi maksudmu

694
00:41:55,291 --> 00:41:57,502
